                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-slate-900">Welcome to Your LSP Companion</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">This guide is designed to help you learn and apply the Lego Serious Play (LSP) methodology without formal certification. Whether you need to run a quick icebreaker, facilitate a deep ideation session, or build the right Lego toolkit, you'll find practical, actionable guidance here.</p>
                    <p class="text-slate-600">Use the tabs above to navigate between the core theory, a library of workshop blueprints, guides for building your toolkit, and links to further resources. The goal is to provide everything you need to start using LSP to foster creativity, communication, and collaboration in your teams.</p>
