            <!-- Foundations Section -->
            <section id="content-foundations" class="content-section animate-fade-in">
                 <div class="bg-white p-6 md:p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2 text-slate-900">Core Principles</h2>
                     <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6 max-w-3xl">LSP is more than just playing with bricks. It's a structured methodology built on a few powerful ideas. Understanding these principles is the first step to becoming an effective facilitator.</p>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
                        <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-blue-200">
                            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-blue-800 mb-2">Thinking with Your Hands</h3>
                            <p class="text-sm text-blue-700">The hand-brain connection unlocks deeper insights than talking alone. Building physical models of abstract ideas externalizes thoughts, leading to new perspectives.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-yellow-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-yellow-200">
                            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-yellow-800 mb-2">The Power of Play</h3>
                            <p class="text-sm text-yellow-700">A playful, safe environment encourages experimentation and creativity, allowing participants to explore ideas without fear of failure.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-green-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-green-200">
                            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-green-800 mb-2">Storytelling & Metaphor</h3>
                            <p class="text-sm text-green-700">Models act as a foundation for stories. Sharing the meaning of a model makes complex ideas tangible, memorable, and easier to discuss.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-red-50 p-6 rounded-lg border border-red-200">
                            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-red-800 mb-2">100% Participation</h3>
                            <p class="text-sm text-red-700">Everyone builds, everyone shares. This democratic approach breaks down hierarchies and ensures every voice is heard and valued.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 mt-10 text-slate-900">The 4-Step Core Process</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 mb-6 max-w-3xl">Every LSP activity, from a 5-minute icebreaker to a 4-hour workshop, follows this simple, iterative cycle. Mastering this flow is key to your facilitation.</p>
                     <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between space-y-4 md:space-y-0 md:space-x-4">
                        <div class="flex-1 text-center bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border">
                            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-500 mb-2">1</div>
                            <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-700">Pose the Question</h3>
                            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Frame a clear, open-ended challenge related to the workshop goal.</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-center text-slate-400 font-mono text-2xl md:rotate-0 rotate-90">&rarr;</div>
                        <div class="flex-1 text-center bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border">
                            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-yellow-500 mb-2">2</div>
                            <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-700">Build the Model</h3>
                            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Participants construct their answer using Lego bricks as metaphors.</p>
                        </div>
                         <div class="flex items-center justify-center text-slate-400 font-mono text-2xl md:rotate-0 rotate-90">&rarr;</div>
                        <div class="flex-1 text-center bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border">
                            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-green-500 mb-2">3</div>
                            <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-700">Share the Story</h3>
                            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Each person explains the meaning behind their model to the group.</p>
                        </div>
                         <div class="flex items-center justify-center text-slate-400 font-mono text-2xl md:rotate-0 rotate-90">&rarr;</div>
                        <div class="flex-1 text-center bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border">
                            <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-500 mb-2">4</div>
                            <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-700">Reflect Together</h3>
                            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">The group discusses patterns, insights, and key takeaways from the models.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
